author: GameSpot
description:
Nagash, the great necromancer himself. Long whispered about in the darkest corners of the lore, he returns with one goal: to drown the world in undeath.
 Lords of the End Times — the next DLC for Total War: WARHAMMER III — is coming Summer 2026.

#totalwar #totalwarwarhammer3 #videogames
title: Total War: WARHAMMER III  - Lords Of The End Times | Cinematic Announcement Trailer

author: GameSpot
description:
We’ve been waiting a long time to say this: Total War is going back to the medieval era ⚔️ Total War: MEDIEVAL III is now in early development!
 
This isn’t just a sequel; it’s the rebirth of historical Total War. And we're bringing you on the journey with us.
